# Gmail Accounts (round-robin, 10/day each)
GMAIL_1=saurabhvy.tech@gmail.com
GMAIL_2=your-second@gmail.com
GMAIL_3=your-third@gmail.com
GMAIL_4=your-fourth@gmail.com

